      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 15-20 min or until all the stock has absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>tomato risotto</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Grate the<strong> cheddar flavour block</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1643194419572-x200.jpg",
